Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.53,0:00:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.21,0:00:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知如此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.66,0:00:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不如繼續對我不理不睬好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.72,0:00:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.37,0:00:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不用察覺到自己對哥哥的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.33,0:00:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不用因知道亞絲娜的事而感到悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.50,0:00:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不用喜歡上拿來代替哥哥的桐人了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.10,0:00:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.96,0:00:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再管我了

Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.52,0:00:54.19,OP2JP,,0000,0000,0000,,隠してた感情が悲鳴を上げてる 確かな誓いを手に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.62,0:01:14.80,OP2JP,,0000,0000,0000,,奇跡だけを求め 消えない闇を彷徨う
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.19,0:01:25.41,OP2JP,,0000,0000,0000,,ここにいれば二度と 未来見る事出来ない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.85,0:01:34.83,OP2JP,,0000,0000,0000,,今宵も月が誘って まだ言葉出せないけど 心の中叫び続けた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.00,0:01:46.23,OP2JP,,0000,0000,0000,,隠してた感情が悲鳴を上げてる 確かな誓いを手に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.47,0:01:51.71,OP2JP,,0000,0000,0000,,あとほんの少しだけ強くなれたなら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.07,0:01:58.06,OP2JP,,0000,0000,0000,,目の前にあるこの空 越えてゆくから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.96,0:02:06.09,OP2JP,,0000,0000,0000,,この先にある未来に手を伸ばすから

Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.52,0:00:54.19,OP2CH,,0000,0000,0000,,壓抑於心中的情感在發出悲鳴 將確切的誓言掌握在手中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.62,0:01:14.80,OP2CH,,0000,0000,0000,,為尋求奇跡 在揮之不去的黑暗中徘徊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.19,0:01:25.41,OP2CH,,0000,0000,0000,,若駐足於此將再也看不見未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.85,0:01:34.83,OP2CH,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚月光再度相邀 雖還未能作聲回應 心中早已百般吶喊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.00,0:01:46.23,OP2CH,,0000,0000,0000,,壓抑於心中的情感在發出悲鳴 將確切的誓言掌握在手中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.47,0:01:51.71,OP2CH,,0000,0000,0000,,倘若能再變強一點
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.07,0:01:58.06,OP2CH,,0000,0000,0000,,我定能飛越眼前的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.96,0:02:06.09,OP2CH,,0000,0000,0000,,朝著前方的未來伸出接納的雙手

Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.94,0:02:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}本字幕由流雲字幕組(http://acgshare.net)所製作\N{\fs28}翻譯：風音 飛翔之櫻 藍山　校對：夢村広宇　時間軸：修　特效：BBA　後期：マモル

Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.95,0:02:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.57,0:02:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那之後
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.98,0:02:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和眼前的家人之間的距離都變得曖昧不清了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.82,0:02:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是這個家庭的親生兒子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.73,0:02:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得知這個事實時年僅10歲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.91,0:02:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人其實是誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.08,0:03:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的認識這個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.35,0:03:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這份異樣感也許正是讓我轉投網路遊戲的理由之一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.76,0:03:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家互不知道對方真實身份的虛擬世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.50,0:03:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沉迷在了這種舒適的世界裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.68,0:03:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在SAO的兩年時間裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.76,0:03:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心境發生了變化
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.84,0:03:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現實世界和假想世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.71,0:03:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩者本質上並無區別
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.15,0:03:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜度對方的身份根本毫無意義
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.76,0:03:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能做的事就只有相信和接受
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.59,0:03:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為自己對某個人的認識
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.84,0:03:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都源於那個人真實的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.68,0:03:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到現實世界後的我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.63,0:03:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著小直的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.32,0:03:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打從心底裡覺得高興
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.94,0:03:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候我發誓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.95,0:04:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要盡全力彌補我和小直這幾年來的隔閡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.58,0:04:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.28,0:04:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能為小直做的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.22,0:04:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小直
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.70,0:04:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在亞倫北部的平臺等你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.06,0:04:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明說了那麼過分的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.74,0:04:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥真是堅強…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.49,0:04:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能像他那麼堅強啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.11,0:04:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.67,0:04:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我鼓勵他不要放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.26,0:04:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.69,0:04:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的我卻在哭泣不已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.12,0:05:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我該說些什麼才好…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.44,0:05:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉琺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.94,0:05:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.02,0:05:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找你好久了 莉琺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.16,0:05:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷…雷根?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.64,0:05:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是被火精靈捉住了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.88,0:05:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把他們全部毒死然後逃了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.61,0:05:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毒死…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.20,0:05:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就跟著莉琺來到了這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.83,0:05:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 話說那個守衛精靈怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.12,0:05:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.26,0:06:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對那個人說了很過分的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.09,0:06:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是決不能說出口的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.00,0:06:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是個笨蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.80,0:06:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 說了些莫名其妙的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.30,0:06:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會再和那個人見面了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.10,0:06:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去蘇伊露風標吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.93,0:06:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉琺…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.53,0:06:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉琺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.17,0:06:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉琺可不能哭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.05,0:06:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.21,0:06:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不一直面帶笑容的話就不是莉琺了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.14,0:06:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我會一直待在你身邊的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.52,0:06:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論在現實還是在這裡我都不會讓你孤身一人的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.59,0:06:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.36,0:06:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.89,0:06:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡莉琺…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.11,0:06:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是直葉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.58,0:06:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.36,0:06:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著 你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.36,0:06:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.91,0:07:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.86,0:07:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順著這套路
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.15,0:07:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來應該是取決於我是否有勇氣告白了才對…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.49,0:07:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.26,0:07:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我偶爾也向你學習一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.69,0:07:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.48,0:07:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小直
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.38,0:07:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 我們來場比試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.54,0:07:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續那天的比試
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.71,0:08:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次我可不會放水了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.80,0:08:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難怪會擺出那樣的架勢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.81,0:08:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.21,0:09:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.62,0:09:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.78,0:09:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想向小直道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.74,0:09:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是卻說不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.52,0:09:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少想受你一劍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.60,0:09:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.94,0:09:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.21,0:09:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.26,0:09:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我其實並沒有真正從那個世界回來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.16,0:09:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情還沒有結束
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.83,0:10:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要她仍未醒來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.30,0:10:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的現實就無法開始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.84,0:10:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我現在還不知道該怎麼對待小直
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.54,0:10:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.48,0:10:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著哥哥真正回到我們家的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.71,0:10:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.26,0:10:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.79,0:10:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.87,0:10:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.50,0:10:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要攻略世界樹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.90,0:10:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他 你 還有我三個人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.59,0:10:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.60,0:10:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結衣在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.74,0:10:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.62,0:10:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你從我和那些守衛的戰鬥中有看出什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.91,0:11:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從狀態上看它們並不算很強大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.18,0:11:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是出現的數量太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.02,0:11:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能說那是被設定成不可能攻略的難度
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.50,0:11:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說總體上和絕對無敵的BOSS是一樣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.07,0:11:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是以爸爸的技能熟練度
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.43,0:11:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞬間突破也不是沒有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.04,0:11:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.97,0:11:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.21,0:11:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能再陪我任性一次嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.39,0:11:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總覺得時間無多了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.90,0:11:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是我能辦到的我都願意做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.39,0:11:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有這傢伙也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.33,0:11:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.57,0:11:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是 畢竟莉琺和我是同心同體的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.54,0:11:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別得意忘形
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.85,0:11:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.93,0:11:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.14,0:12:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝大家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.82,0:12:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守衛由我來應付
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.85,0:12:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果只是在後方治療我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.90,0:12:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該不用擔心被攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.08,0:12:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.41,0:13:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.74,0:13:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這敵人的數量…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.44,0:13:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒完沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.08,0:13:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷根
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.10,0:13:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.17,0:13:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我們會被設為攻擊目標
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.89,0:14:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是它們的運算程序不同於外面的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.00,0:14:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣區分前衛和後衛就沒有意義了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.15,0:14:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.19,0:14:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷根?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.97,0:14:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉琺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.10,0:14:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是很明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.93,0:14:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是很重要的事對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.02,0:14:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.59,0:14:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許就現在來說這不是在玩遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.59,0:14:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來想辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.19,0:14:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷根?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.42,0:14:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.73,0:14:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.72,0:15:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷根
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.64,0:15:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了 快逃到外面去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.92,0:15:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…暗屬性魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.96,0:15:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自爆魔法?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.83,0:15:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這要受到多大的死亡懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.55,0:15:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的是個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.95,0:16:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.07,0:16:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.74,0:16:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辦不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.15,0:16:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情…這種事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.18,0:16:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風精靈部隊?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.02,0:16:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.63,0:16:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛龍?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.99,0:16:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是貓妖的龍騎部隊?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.78,0:17:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.20,0:17:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.41,0:17:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,備齊裝備花了好多時間呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.65,0:17:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朔夜 亞麗莎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.62,0:17:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍騎部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.08,0:17:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍息攻擊準備
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.69,0:17:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風精靈部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.93,0:17:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,極限攻擊準備
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.53,0:17:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火焰吐息 噴射
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.28,0:17:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芬裡爾風暴 釋放
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.94,0:17:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.24,0:17:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝兩位
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.11,0:17:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用道謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.63,0:17:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可是欠了那位守護精靈一份大人情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.83,0:17:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且全靠他那大筆資金我們才得以完成攻略的準備
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.23,0:18:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全體突擊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.03,0:18:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要畏縮 向前挺進
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.42,0:18:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小直
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.11,0:18:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背後就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.46,0:18:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.57,0:19:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊隨他們兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.72,0:19:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.85,0:19:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.77,0:19:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.34,0:19:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.52,0:20:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全體掉頭 撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.07,0:20:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.99,0:20:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遍及每一個角落
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.21,0:20:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直…一直翱翔於蒼穹之下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.79,0:20:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到世界的中心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.13,0:20:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.96,0:20:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.29,0:20:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結衣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.15,0:20:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.08,0:20:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.41,0:21:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這扇門不是由任務系統鎖定的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.94,0:21:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是以系統管理員權限鎖定的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.14,0:21:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.09,0:21:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說玩家是無法打開這扇門的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.56,0:21:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.24,0:21:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.74,0:21:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.33,0:21:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結衣 用這個試試
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.14,0:21:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始轉寫代碼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.51,0:22:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始傳送
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.86,0:22:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 把手給我

Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.73,0:22:22.54,ED2JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}高く高く この手を伸ばして
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.85,0:22:26.60,ED2JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}きっと きっと って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.71,0:22:32.42,ED2JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}もう一度願うから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.91,0:22:47.07,ED2JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}とめどない想いは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.50,0:22:50.58,ED2JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}日常に飲まれて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.10,0:22:53.96,ED2JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}揺らめきながらまた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.04,0:22:57.69,ED2JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}形を変えていった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.26,0:23:01.39,ED2JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}今さらもう遅いかな
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.80,0:23:04.84,ED2JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}返事のない自問自答
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.33,0:23:08.22,ED2JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}すべてはそう自分次第
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.35,0:23:12.53,ED2JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}終わりも始まりも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.05,0:23:19.74,ED2JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}高く高く この手を伸ばして
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.01,0:23:26.91,ED2JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}優しい光を目指して羽ばたくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.12,0:23:34.16,ED2JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}心に灯した情熱を抱いて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.51,0:23:38.30,ED2JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}きっと きっと って
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.33,0:23:42.50,ED2JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}もう一度願うから

Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.73,0:22:22.54,ED2CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}更高更高向著那蒼穹伸出手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.85,0:22:26.60,ED2CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}我會默念著承諾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.71,0:22:32.42,ED2CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}再度祈願
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.91,0:22:47.07,ED2CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}永無止息的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.50,0:22:50.58,ED2CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}被日常所湮沒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.10,0:22:53.96,ED2CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}在搖曳中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.04,0:22:57.69,ED2CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}再次改變了姿態
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.26,0:23:01.39,ED2CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}事到如今是否已太遲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.80,0:23:04.84,ED2CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}我向著虛空自問自答道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.33,0:23:08.22,ED2CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}其實一切都取決於自己
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.35,0:23:12.53,ED2CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}無論終結還是開始
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.05,0:23:19.74,ED2CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}更高更高向著那蒼穹伸出手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.01,0:23:26.91,ED2CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}朝著那溫和的光芒展翅翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.12,0:23:34.16,ED2CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}也不忘擁緊那燃點於心中的熱情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.51,0:23:38.30,ED2CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}我會默念著承諾
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.33,0:23:42.50,ED2CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}再度祈願

Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.11,0:23:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 鍍金的勇者